{"tid":2368921,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"冬季K2已被成功攀登攻破","createTime":"2021-01-16T15:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T05:03:56.000Z","uid":220089,"like":142,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"8397f85a4df6b4936b4acd0306719e725ecbdae0","tid":2368921,"uid":220089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:21:05.000Z","msg":"冬季K2一直都係登山界嘅難題，亦都係唯一一座8千米高山未有人成功係冬季登頂，而係今日下午5點，尼泊爾有兩隊登山隊合作 Nims+ Mingma G成功登頂冬季既K2，寫下人類歷史新嘅一頁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9VXjN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT9VXjN5.jpg&h=e776c521&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88sZx76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88sZx76.jpg&h=b5e23431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 冬季攀登K2歷史<br />\n<br />\n1987/1988: Polish-Canadian-British Expedition- 7,300 meters.<br />\n<br />\n2002/2003: Netia K2 Polish Winter Expedition - 7,650 meters.<br />\n<br />\n2011/2012:  Russian expedition - 7,200 meters.<br />\n<br />\n2017/2018: Polish National Winter Expedition- 7600 meters.<br />\n<br />\n2020/2021: Nepalese K2 Winter Expedition (combined) - 8611 METERS (SUMMIT 🏔)<br />\n<br />\n10 climbers<br />\na. Nirmal Purja <br />\nb. Gelje Sherpa<br />\nc. Mingma David Sherpa<br />\nd. Mingma G<br />\ne. Sona Sherpa<br />\nf. Mingma Tenzi Sherpa<br />\ng. Pem Chhiri Sherpa<br />\nh. Dawa Temba Sherpa<br />\ni. Kili Pemba Sherpa<br />\nj. Dawa Tenjing Sherpa<br />\n<br />\n得一個唔係Sherpa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9800cac75a83e034fbc304b7be5174ecf3ad56a","tid":2368921,"uid":3122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a1efbd6133d678010d567f651f9da69df68d07","tid":2368921,"uid":38465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:23:02.000Z","msg":"巴打會唔會爬呢座"},{"pid":"247099c0b0e2c